NAME: gwit

DESCRIPTION: 
`gwit` or Gtk tWITter client is an open source twitter client made with usability in mind. gwit uses pyGtk <http://www.pygtk.org/> and python-twoauth <http://www.techno-st.net/python-twoauth/> library.

WWW: http://dev.tsukuba-linux.org/gwit

INSTALL: see INSTALL

LICENCE: `gwit` is licensed under GNU General Public License (GPL) version 3. Please refer to COPYING for more information.

BUGS:
Patches / bug reports should be submitted to the core developer at techno@tsukuba-linux.org

AUTHOR(S):
This project is part of the "TsukuLUG Make" from University of Tsukuba Linux User Group <http://www.tsukuba-linux.org/>

